data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Nestled on a stunning 1.2-acre lot, this 4-bedroom, 2-and-a-half bathroom gem is a masterpiece waiting to be discovered. As you step inside, you're greeted by the warmth of a home that's not just a dwelling but a haven of comfort and style. The split foyer design of this home adds a unique touch, creating a sense of openness and flow. But that's not all a the basement boasts not one, but two finished bonus rooms! Imagine the possibilities a one as your personalized home office, the other as a vibrant rec room where memories are made.    What sets this home apart? No rental restrictions and no HOA! That's right a the freedom to make this space truly yours without the constraints of rental limitations or HOA regulations. Let your creativity run wild as you envision and personalize each room to reflect your unique style.
